[ ] CARD.2  [P2] ADD BLUR-UP IMAGE PLACEHOLDER
     Currently: Images use loading="lazy" but pop in abruptly with no
     placeholder.
     Enhance: Add a low-res blurred placeholder or solid color background
     that transitions to the full image on load. Use a CSS aspect-ratio
     box to prevent layout shift.

[ ] CARD.3  [P2] DISABLE HOVER TRANSFORM ON TOUCH DEVICES
